793
00:41:41,199 --> 00:41:43,234
A halálig.

794
00:41:43,301 --> 00:41:44,836
Csak néha gyorsabb.

795
00:41:44,970 --> 00:41:47,172
- Mi bajod van? - Fúj.

796
00:41:47,272 --> 00:41:49,074
